high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the cabinets above the microwave, to your right.
Pull out a bowl from the left cabinet above the microwave.
Turn around and go towards the wall, to the refrigerator on your left.
Place the bowl in the center of the top shelf of the refrigerator for a moment to chill, then remove the bowl from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the right end of the kitchen island.
Place the bowl on the right side of the kitchen island.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold bowl on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Turn left and head to the microwave above the stove
Open the microwave and take out the bowl
Turn left and walk forward head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in the bowl then take it out
Turn right then walk forward face the table on your right
Put the bowl on the right side of the table
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled bowl on the table

high_descs: Turn left, go to the stove, turn right to face the stove.
Pick up the bowl in the cabinet above the stove.
Bring the bowl to the fridge behind you on the right.
Chill the bowl in the fridge.
Bring the chilled bowl to the green table behind you.
Put the chilled bowl on the green table, on the right side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on the green table.
